 S&P, Fitch and DBRS)=C2=A0to Aaa/AA+/AA+/AAA probably doesn=E2=80=99t matt=
er=C2=A0that=C2=A0much.
So that leaves Option 2: If Fitch, or whoever, downgrades the US government=
