 safe. Which makes bank accounts=C2=A0relatively more attractive, even if t=
hey pay less.=C2=A0Last week Bloomberg=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31597233.273415/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
